<h2>Create a new password</h2>
<br>
<% if @provider == 'shopify' %>
  <p>You (or someone else) entered this email address when trying to create a new password for this <%= Settings.app_name %> account.</p>
  <br>
  <p>However this user doesn't have a username or password, they log in through a Shopify account. Go to your Shopify admin > Apps > <%= Settings.app_name %> to log in.</p>
  <br>
  <p>If you did not request a new password, simply ignore this email.</p>
  <br>
<% else %>
  <p><%= @username %>, <a href="<%= @password_reset_url %>?utm_source=new-password&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=create-password">press this link to create a new password for your <%= Settings.app_name %> account</a>.</p>
  <br>
  <p>If you didn't request this or don't want to create a new password simply ignore this email: nothing will be changed.</p>
  <br>
  <a target='_blank' href="<%= @password_reset_url %>?utm_source=new-password&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=create-password" class='link2' style='color:#ffffff'>CREATE A NEW PASSWORD</a>
  <br>
<% end %>
